snippet: Justin Wilson was the surprise winner Saturday night at Texas Motor Speedway, where Graham Rahal wrecked while leading a topsy-turvy race that took out several contenders.
abstract: Justin Wilson wins for the first time since 2009 after Graham Rahal hit the wall while leading at Texas Motor Speedway in the IndyCar race in Fort Worth; other auto racing results noted.
lead_paragraph: Justin Wilson was the surprise winner Saturday night at Texas Motor Speedway, where Graham Rahal wrecked while leading a topsy-turvy race that took out several contenders.

headline.seo: Wilson Wins Indy Car Race After Rahal Hits Wall at Texas Motor Speedway
headline.main: Wilson Wins After Rahal Hits Wall at Texas Motor Speedway
headline.print_headline: Wilson Wins After Rahal Hits Wall
